          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/729.-step-7.-new-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> and serve it on top of the<strong> creamy mushroom sauce</strong>, with the <strong>mashed potato</strong> and <strong>Chantenay carrots</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
